| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4483 — Recovery Inhibition (anubis)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27fd6034-3620-53d7-b8b8-b78431f4f24c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
